  description="Kitchen lighting design guide for Seattle homes. Task, ambient, accent lighting, under-cabinet LEDs, pendant islands, recessed lighting, and natural light tips for the Pacific Northwest."
  canonical={`${SITE.url}/blog/kitchen-lighting-design-guide/`}
